---
/**
 * Legacy long-form homepage content (English).
 * Kept intentionally to preserve existing long text.
 * Updated with Accordion components for better UX.
 */
import Accordion from '../Accordion.astro';
import AccordionGroup from '../AccordionGroup.astro';
import AudioPlayer from '../AudioPlayer.astro';
import OptimizedImage from '../OptimizedImage.astro';
import { HOMEPAGE_SOUNDS } from '../../data/sounds';
---

    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About Fiddlebops Incredibox</h2>
            <AccordionGroup>
                <Accordion title="I. Fiddlebops Basic Information & Gameplay" defaultOpen={true}>
                    <p><strong>Game Name:</strong> Fiddlebops</p>
                    <p><strong>Genre/Tags:</strong> Music Creation, Rhythm, Experimental, Educational, Family Friendly, Casual, Singleplayer, Creative</p>
                    <p><strong>Platforms:</strong> Web (Browser)</p>
                    <p><strong>Release Date:</strong> Approx. November 7, 2024</p>
                    <p><strong>Price/Access:</strong> Free</p>
                    <hr>
                    <h4>1. Creation Mechanics</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Core Mechanic:</strong> Select cute Fiddlebops characters, each representing a unique instrument sound or musical element. Combine sounds by dragging and dropping characters onto performance spots or a timeline.</li>
                        <li><strong>Sound Combination:</strong> Combine multiple Fiddlebops for multi-layered music. Different combinations yield varied musical textures.</li>
                        <li><strong>Rhythm & Timing:</strong> Likely uses a grid-based placement or simple timeline for controlling sound timing and rhythm.</li>
                        <li><strong>Looping & Repetition:</strong> May include mechanisms for looping sounds to create repeating musical phrases.</li>
                        <li><strong>Exploration & Experimentation:</strong> Encourages free exploration of sound combinations, emphasizing creative fun.</li>
                    </ul>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="II. Fiddlebops Modding & Community Content">
                    <h4>1. Overview of Popular Game Mods</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/fiddlebops-but-sprunki/">Fiddlebops but Sprunki</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/fiddlebops-fix/">Fiddlebops Fix</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/fiddlebops-polos/">Fiddlebops Polos</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/fiddlebops-but-dandys-world/">Fiddlebops But Dandy's World</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>2. Character Introductions & Community Creations</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Character Introductions:</strong> The Fiddlebops are cute, colorful cartoon characters, each linked to a specific sound/instrument.
                            <ul>
                                <li><em>Drummer-type characters:</em> Provide rhythmic sections.</li>
                                <li><em>Melody-type characters:</em> Offer sounds like flutes, keyboards, or synth leads.</li>
                                <li><em>Chord/Bass-type characters:</em> Supply background harmonies or basslines.</li>
                                <li><em>Sound Effect-type characters:</em> Emit special effects or vocal samples.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Community Creations:</strong> Primarily involves players creating and sharing their musical pieces made with "Fiddlebops." These are shared on platforms like itch / scratch comments, forums, and social media (YouTube, TikTok, Twitter with #Fiddlebops).</li>
                    </ul>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="III. How To Play Fiddlebops">
                    <h4>1. Selecting Characters</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Players choose from a library of Fiddlebops characters, each with a unique look and sound.</li>
                        <li>Sound previews may be available when clicking or dragging a character.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>2. Combining Sounds</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Players drag and drop selected Fiddlebops onto designated areas in the game interface.</li>
                        <li>Multiple Fiddlebops can be placed to play sounds simultaneously.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>3. Mixing & Creating</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Players alter music structure, rhythm, and melody by adjusting Fiddlebop placement and quantity.</li>
                        <li>The game might offer simple controls (e.g., volume adjustment), but focuses on the joy of combination.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>4. Sharing Creations</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The game itself may not have built-in recording/sharing features.</li>
                        <li>Players typically use third-party screen recording software to capture and share their work on various online platforms.</li>
                    </ul>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="IV. Fiddlebops Features">
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Intuitive & Accessible:</strong> Designed for all ages, especially beginners, with simple controls.</li>
                        <li><strong>Encourages Creativity:</strong> A platform for free experimentation with sound.</li>
                        <li><strong>Cute & Unique Visual Style:</strong> Brightly colored with adorable character designs.</li>
                        <li><strong>Experimental Music Experience:</strong> Discover unexpected sound combinations.</li>
                        <li><strong>Educational Value:</strong> Introduces basic music elements in a fun way.</li>
                        <li><strong>Stress-Free Creation:</strong> No win/loss conditions or scoring.</li>
                        <li><strong>Free or Name Your Own Price:</strong> Low barrier to entry.</li>
                    </ul>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="V. Fiddlebops Download & Experience">
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Main Platform:</strong> <a href="https://www.playfiddlebops.com/fiddlebops">playfiddlebops.com</a> or itch and scratch.</li>
                        <li><strong>Experience Recommendation:</strong> Try the web version first; download desktop version for smoother/offline play.</li>
                    </ul>
                </Accordion>
            </AccordionGroup>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="games sound-explorer-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Explore the Different Sounds in Fiddlebops Incredibox</h2>
            <div class="sound-grid">
                {HOMEPAGE_SOUNDS.map((sound) => (
                    <div class="sound-card">
                        <div class="sound-card__image">
                            <OptimizedImage src={sound.imageSrc} alt={sound.title} loading="lazy" width={150} height={150} />
                        </div>
                        <p class="sound-card__title">{sound.title}</p>
                        <AudioPlayer src={sound.audioSrc} title={sound.title} />
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="game-video about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Fiddlebops Incredibox Game Video</h2>
            <div class="video-container">
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4Oj-dVLSA70" title="Fiddlebops ALL POLOS 4K (WITH SUBTITLES)" loading="lazy" width="560" height="315" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JlMa-fRBOwE" title="Every Incredibox Fiddlebops in 8 Minutes" loading="lazy" width="560" height="315" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture;" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                <div class="clear-both"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="clear-both"></div>
    </section>

    <div class="clear-both"></div>

    <section class="about faq-section" id="faq">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>FAQ About Fiddlebops Incredibox</h2>
            <AccordionGroup exclusive={true}>
                <Accordion title="What is the Fiddlebops Incredibox Game?" defaultOpen={true}>
                    <p>
                        The Fiddlebops game is a fan-made project inspired by Incredibox. Here, you can experience the fun of mixing sounds and create unique musical pieces through an intuitive interface.
                    </p>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="Is the Fiddlebops Incredibox Free?">
                    <p>
                        Yes, the Fiddlebops Incredibox is completely free. Players can play online without downloading.
                    </p>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="Do I Need to Download or Install Fiddlebops?">
                    <p>
                        No. The game runs directly in your browser and supports both desktop and mobile devices.
                    </p>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="Do I need a musical background to play?">
                    <p>
                        Not at all! Fiddlebops Incredibox is designed precisely so that people without a musical background can easily create music. It's more like a sound toy and creative tool.
                    </p>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="How Do I Start Creating Music?">
                    <p>
                        Players can start by dragging characters onto the stage, combining their unique sounds into a musical piece. Experimenting with different character combinations can unlock hidden melodies and bonus content.
                    </p>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="Is the Game Suitable for Music Enthusiasts?">
                    <p>
                        Absolutely! Fiddlebops provides a platform full of creativity and fun for music enthusiasts.
                    </p>
                </Accordion>

                <Accordion title="Does the Game Support Multiplayer Collaboration?">
                    <p>
                        Yes, players can collaborate with others in real-time to co-create music.
                    </p>
                </Accordion>
            </AccordionGroup>
        </div>
    </section>
